data.description: Open the doors to wide open space in this 3,000 (+) Sq. Ft. home! Adorned with an over-sized island, the kitchen is dressed to impress with new cabinets, built in gas cook top, built in oven and dishwasher. On the main floor, enjoy 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms along with a larger living room and dining combo. On the upper floor, the master and en suite is private with an additional room for an office, private seating area or turn it into a large closet. The basement offers plenty of storage and two extra rooms without legal egress windows. Sitting on 0.25 acres, this property has a double car attached garage, good parking, two sheds and alley access. This is a must see home!
